Template: custom-conf-postgresql/bind-address
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Bind to a specific address(es) ?
 Please specify which address(es) to bind the service to:
 .
  - {empty}:   do not bind to any specific address (security risk)
  - localhost: bind to localhost addresses (private service)
  - gateway:   bind to addresses matching configured gateway/network
  - <addr>:    space-separated actual IP address(es)

Template: custom-conf-postgresql/ssl-enable
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Enable SSL/TLS (requires valid certificate) ?

